A man named Malik Wakili has been arrested by the Economic and Financial Crimes Commission for pulling an internet scam against Babatunde Raji Fashola, former Lagos governor, and current works and housing minister. The man who will be arraigned today by the EFCC swindled Fashola of N3.1million, PM News reports. The arraignment is pending before Justice Chukwujekwu Aneke. Details emerging.